      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Imagine the sun dipping below the horizon as you glide through winding coastal roads, the engine singing a symphony only a classic of this caliber can perform. This isn't just a car; it's a time capsule of elegance and raw power. Every curve of its hand-polished body reflects a legacy of prestige, while the interior welcomes you with the rich, unmistakable scent of fine craftsmanship. To drive it is to command the very spirit of the open road\u2014a rare opportunity to own a masterpiece that feels as vital today as the moment it first left the showroom floor.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
